ugivorous phyllostomids on the basis of dietary specialization on core plant taxa with chiropterochorous fruits.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "S\u00e1nchez, Mariano S.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Giannini, Norberto P.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Barquez, Rub\u00e9n M.", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/05b6a48d3c51521b62e6b8167204e453", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/6567dcfdd160699fb880d3d463c547f034d0fe930c5e82b579815c59a963a0b5", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/C8UWXB5T", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/C8UWXB5T", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/757f6c7fb34c1963ec3e3dc705090fd6!/b10901-13464", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "1", "pages": "22-31", "title": "Mammalian Biology", "volume": "77"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/05b6a48d3c51521b62e6b8167204e453"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:C8UWXB5T"}, {"identifier": "10.1016/j.mambio.2011.06.002"}], "communities": [{"id": "batlit"}, {"id": "biosyslit"}], "relations": {"version": [{"index": 0, "is_last": true, "parent": {"pid_type": "recid", "pid_value": "14817055"}}]}}, "title": "Bat frugivor